title: Battle.of.the.Empires[2013]EngDub.5.1.DvDrip.x264-r3mnants
description:
Notes:
Some reason the beginning of the movie has a foreign language but the rest of the movie is dubbed in English. This isn't my fault and is this way on the DVD itself.

A young and ambitious sultan ascends to the top of the Ottoman throne, desperately seeking more power for his nation. Braving his enemies, he attempts the unthinkable and courageously tries to conquer Constantinople for his people. After marching his heroic group of warriors straight towards Constantinople, the resulting battle is one of the greatest and most brutal sieges anyone will ever witness.
